Q4. Running Max Salary
From the employees table, ordered by hire_date, show the highest salary seen so far at each point (running maximum). Show: hire_date, name, salary, and running_max_salary.

select hire_date,name,salary,max(salary) over (order by hire_date) as running_max_salary
from employees
