 Running Total as % of Final Total
From daily_sales, show each day's running total and what percentage of the grand total has been reached by that day. Round the percentage to 2 decimal places.

💡 Hint
⚡ Running SUM ÷ Grand Total

select sale_date,amount,  sum(amount) over (order by sale_date) as running_total,
sum(amount) over () as grand_total
, round(sum(amount) over (order by sale_date)*100.0/sum(amount) over (),2) as pct_running_total
from daily_sales
